init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: you can't come up with anything.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Oh, he's not here right now, but I can take a message."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I want you to continue my legacy, and I want you to do it my way."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm going to send you a letter every day, and you're going to follow my instructions to the letter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I want you to start by doing something that I never did.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I want you to go to a gun store and buy a gun.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I want you to go to a shooting range and learn how to use it.
